description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced HR professional to lead our HR operational activities including recruitment, temporary staffing, medical staffing and our performance team. This is a crucial role for the department requiring &lt;span&gt;delivery of a high quality, comprehensive service. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Extensive experience in high volume recruitment, understanding service demand and translating into actionable marketing plans, campaigns, and employer branding is an essential requirement as is the ability to develop strong working relationships, both internally and externally. You should also have experience of&lt;span&gt; developing pay and reward strategies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be managing a team of dedicated staff who seek to deliver exceptional customer service, and will be a member of the Senior Management Team, supporting us in ensuring people are at the heart of everything we do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note, this vacancy is subject to job evaluation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Claire Webster&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Deputy Director of Workforce &amp; OD&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address claire.webster@sussexpartnership.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 07471 032089&lt;/p&gt;
